{The bidding has been as shown.   

You have 16 HCP and two more points for the fifth and sixth \Hs. That is too strong for a simple overcall. Instead you double. Partner responds 2\C.  

You bid 2\H, describing your hand as a 1-suited hand, too strong to merely overcall. Partner bids the \H game and you pass.}

